data.description: Nestled within the picturesque Waterfall community, this exquisite custom home is an absolute must-see. Step into a world of luxury and convenience, with an open great room seamlessly merging into a designer kitchen. The heart of the home boasts a generous butler's pantry and custom cabinetry, offering both style and functionality. This home's layout is designed with your comfort in mind, featuring a thoughtfully crafted split floor plan with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths. For those seeking extra space and versatility, a loft awaits, and an oversized garage accommodates two cars and a golf cart with ease. Beyond your private retreat, the community itself is a hidden treasure. With remarkably low POA fees, residents enjoy access to an 8.5-acre stocked lake, perfect for tranquil fishing and non-gasoline motor boating. Launching your watercraft is effortless with a convenient boat ramp. Stay active and fit with on-site amenities that include a well-equipped fitness room and a refreshing pool. For outdoor enthusiasts, a serene one-mile circle awaits your walking, running, or biking adventures, free from the hustle and bustle of traffic. Location is everything, and this property doesn't disappoint. Situated a mere 8 minutes from the beachfront, 5 minutes from the vibrant Main Street, and less than a mile from the new North Myrtle Beach Sports Park and SC 31. You'll find peace and security within the confines of this gated community, characterized by its all-brick homes and privacy walls. This home expertly combines prime location and top-notch quality, offering a unique opportunity that you simply can't afford to miss. All measurements are approximate and not guaranteed; the buyer is responsible for verification.
